-- Turkey's Bank Asya says exclusivity deal with QIB annulled
-- 
-- Fri Aug 08, 2014 03:02AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Aug 8 (Reuters) - Turkish Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> said on Friday an exclusive deal with Qatar Islamic Bank (QIB) to acquire a stake in the Turkish lender was annulled as of August 8.

The lender said in a statement to the Istanbul stock exchange that the exclusivity deal with QIB was terminated in order to receive formal bids from domestic investors.